## Education
### Doctoral candidate in Computer Science
I was raised in Honduras and at the moment I am living in Germany. As of 07.2023 I am a doctoral researcher at the Cluster of Excellence, SimTech in Stuttgart. Soon I will be joining TU Dortmund and I will be working with [Prof. Dr. Paul Bürkner](https://paul-buerkner.github.io) in Computational Statistics. In general, I am interested in Bayesian Inference, Prior specification, Probabilistic Programming and High Dimensional Statistics.
